{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.1","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 3:1","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.002.046,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Mariage de Salomon avec la fille du roi d\u2019\u00c9gypte. Le songe de Salomon<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-15: cf. (2 Ch 1:1-13. 1 R 4:29-34.) Ps 119:125. (Ja 1:5. Mt 6:33.) 1 Co 14:12.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.3.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Salomon s\u2019allia par mariage avec Pharaon, roi d\u2019\u00c9gypte. Il prit pour femme la fille de Pharaon, et il l\u2019amena dans la ville de David, jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce qu\u2019il e\u00fbt achev\u00e9 de b\u00e2tir sa maison, la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, et le mur d\u2019enceinte de J\u00e9rusalem.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3","name":"1 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.2","name":"1 Rois 3:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.2.46","name":"1 Rois 2:46","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.2.46"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.2","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 3:2","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.3.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Le peuple ne sacrifiait que sur les hauts lieux, car jusqu\u2019\u00e0 cette \u00e9poque il n\u2019avait point \u00e9t\u00e9 b\u00e2ti de maison au nom de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3","name":"1 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.3","name":"1 Rois 3:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.1","name":"1 Rois 3:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.3","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 3:3","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.3.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Salomon aimait l\u2019\u00c9ternel, et suivait les coutumes de David, son p\u00e8re. Seulement c\u2019\u00e9tait sur les hauts lieux qu\u2019il offrait des sacrifices et des parfums.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3","name":"1 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.4","name":"1 Rois 3:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.2","name":"1 Rois 3:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.4","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 3:4","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.3.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Le roi se rendit \u00e0 Gabaon pour y sacrifier, car c\u2019\u00e9tait le principal des hauts lieux. Salomon offrit mille holocaustes sur l\u2019autel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3","name":"1 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.5","name":"1 Rois 3:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.3","name":"1 Rois 3:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.5","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 3:5","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.3.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>A Gabaon, l\u2019\u00c9ternel apparut en songe \u00e0 Salomon pendant la nuit, et Dieu lui dit: Demande ce que tu veux que je te donne.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3","name":"1 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.6","name":"1 Rois 3:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.4","name":"1 Rois 3:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.6","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 3:6","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.3.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Salomon r\u00e9pondit: Tu as trait\u00e9 avec une grande bienveillance ton serviteur David, mon p\u00e8re, parce qu\u2019il marchait en ta pr\u00e9sence dans la fid\u00e9lit\u00e9, dans la justice, et dans la droiture de c\u0153ur envers toi; tu lui as conserv\u00e9 cette grande bienveillance, et tu lui as donn\u00e9 un fils qui est assis sur son tr\u00f4ne, comme on le voit aujourd\u2019hui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3","name":"1 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.7","name":"1 Rois 3:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.5","name":"1 Rois 3:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.7","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 3:7","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.3.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Maintenant, \u00c9ternel mon Dieu, tu as fait r\u00e9gner ton serviteur \u00e0 la place de David, mon p\u00e8re; et moi je ne suis qu\u2019un jeune homme, je n\u2019ai point d\u2019exp\u00e9rience.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3","name":"1 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.8","name":"1 Rois 3:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.6","name":"1 Rois 3:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.8","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 3:8","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.3.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Ton serviteur est au milieu du peuple que tu as choisi, peuple immense, qui ne peut \u00eatre ni compt\u00e9 ni nombr\u00e9, \u00e0 cause de sa multitude.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3","name":"1 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.9","name":"1 Rois 3:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.7","name":"1 Rois 3:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.9","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 3:9","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.3.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Accorde donc \u00e0 ton serviteur un c\u0153ur intelligent pour juger ton peuple, pour discerner le bien du mal! Car qui pourrait juger ton peuple, ce peuple si nombreux?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3","name":"1 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.10","name":"1 Rois 3:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.8","name":"1 Rois 3:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.10","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 3:10","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.3.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Cette demande de Salomon plut au Seigneur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3","name":"1 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.11","name":"1 Rois 3:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.9","name":"1 Rois 3:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.11","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 3:11","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.3.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Et Dieu lui dit: Puisque c\u2019est l\u00e0 ce que tu demandes, puisque tu ne demandes pour toi ni une longue vie, ni les richesses, ni la mort de tes ennemis, et que tu demandes de l\u2019intelligence pour exercer la justice,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3","name":"1 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.12","name":"1 Rois 3:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.10","name":"1 Rois 3:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.12","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 3:12","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.3.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>voici, j\u2019agirai selon ta parole. Je te donnerai un c\u0153ur sage et intelligent, de telle sorte qu\u2019il n\u2019y aura eu personne avant toi et qu\u2019on ne verra jamais personne de semblable \u00e0 toi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3","name":"1 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.13","name":"1 Rois 3:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.11","name":"1 Rois 3:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.13","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 3:13","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.3.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Je te donnerai, en outre, ce que tu n\u2019as pas demand\u00e9, des richesses et de la gloire, de telle sorte qu\u2019il n\u2019y aura pendant toute ta vie aucun roi qui soit ton pareil.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3","name":"1 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.14","name":"1 Rois 3:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.12","name":"1 Rois 3:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.14","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 3:14","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.3.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Et si tu marches dans mes voies, en observant mes lois et mes commandements, comme l\u2019a fait David, ton p\u00e8re, je prolongerai tes jours.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3","name":"1 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.15","name":"1 Rois 3:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.13","name":"1 Rois 3:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.15","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 3:15","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.3.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Salomon s\u2019\u00e9veilla. Et voil\u00e0 le songe. Salomon revint \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem, et se pr\u00e9senta devant l\u2019arche de l\u2019alliance de l\u2019\u00c9ternel. Il offrit des holocaustes et des sacrifices d\u2019actions de gr\u00e2ces, et il fit un festin \u00e0 tous ses serviteurs.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3","name":"1 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.16","name":"1 Rois 3:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.14","name":"1 Rois 3:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.16","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 3:16","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.017,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Le jugement de Salomon<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 16-28: cf. Ps 72:1-4. Pr 25:2; 16:10. (Lu 12:2. Ro 2:16.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.3.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Alors deux femmes prostitu\u00e9es vinrent chez le roi, et se pr\u00e9sent\u00e8rent devant lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3","name":"1 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.17","name":"1 Rois 3:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.15","name":"1 Rois 3:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.17","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 3:17","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.3.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>L\u2019une des femmes dit: Pardon! Mon seigneur, moi et cette femme nous demeurions dans la m\u00eame maison, et je suis accouch\u00e9e pr\u00e8s d\u2019elle dans la maison.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3","name":"1 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.18","name":"1 Rois 3:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.16","name":"1 Rois 3:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.18","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 3:18","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.3.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Trois jours apr\u00e8s, cette femme est aussi accouch\u00e9e. Nous habitions ensemble, aucun \u00e9tranger n\u2019\u00e9tait avec nous dans la maison, il n\u2019y avait que nous deux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3","name":"1 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.19","name":"1 Rois 3:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.17","name":"1 Rois 3:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.19","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 3:19","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.3.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Le fils de cette femme est mort pendant la nuit, parce qu\u2019elle s\u2019\u00e9tait couch\u00e9e sur lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3","name":"1 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.20","name":"1 Rois 3:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.18","name":"1 Rois 3:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.20","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 3:20","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.3.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Elle s\u2019est lev\u00e9e au milieu de la nuit, elle a pris mon fils \u00e0 mes c\u00f4t\u00e9s tandis que ta servante dormait, et elle l\u2019a couch\u00e9 dans son sein; et son fils qui \u00e9tait mort, elle l\u2019a couch\u00e9 dans mon sein.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3","name":"1 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.21","name":"1 Rois 3:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.19","name":"1 Rois 3:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.21","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 3:21","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.3.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Le matin, je me suis lev\u00e9e pour allaiter mon fils; et voici, il \u00e9tait mort. Je l\u2019ai regard\u00e9 attentivement le matin; et voici, ce n\u2019\u00e9tait pas mon fils que j\u2019avais enfant\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3","name":"1 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.22","name":"1 Rois 3:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.20","name":"1 Rois 3:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.22","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 3:22","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.3.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>L\u2019autre femme dit: Au contraire! C\u2019est mon fils qui est vivant, et c\u2019est ton fils qui est mort. Mais la premi\u00e8re r\u00e9pliqua: Nullement! C\u2019est ton fils qui est mort, et c\u2019est mon fils qui est vivant. C\u2019est ainsi qu\u2019elles parl\u00e8rent devant le roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3","name":"1 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.23","name":"1 Rois 3:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.21","name":"1 Rois 3:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.23","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 3:23","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.3.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Le roi dit: L\u2019une dit: C\u2019est mon fils qui est vivant, et c\u2019est ton fils qui est mort; et l\u2019autre dit: Nullement! C\u2019est ton fils qui est mort, et c\u2019est mon fils qui est vivant.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3","name":"1 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.24","name":"1 Rois 3:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.22","name":"1 Rois 3:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.24","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 3:24","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.3.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Puis il ajouta: Apportez-moi une \u00e9p\u00e9e. On apporta une \u00e9p\u00e9e devant le roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3","name":"1 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.25","name":"1 Rois 3:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.23","name":"1 Rois 3:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.25","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 3:25","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.3.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Et le roi dit: Coupez en deux l\u2019enfant qui vit, et donnez-en la moiti\u00e9 \u00e0 l\u2019une et la moiti\u00e9 \u00e0 l\u2019autre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3","name":"1 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.26","name":"1 Rois 3:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.24","name":"1 Rois 3:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.26","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 3:26","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.3.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Alors la femme dont le fils \u00e9tait vivant sentit ses entrailles s\u2019\u00e9mouvoir pour son fils, et elle dit au roi: Ah! Mon seigneur, donnez-lui l\u2019enfant qui vit, et ne le faites point mourir. Mais l\u2019autre dit: Il ne sera ni \u00e0 moi ni \u00e0 toi; coupez-le!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3","name":"1 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.27","name":"1 Rois 3:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.25","name":"1 Rois 3:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.27","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 3:27","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.3.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Et le roi, prenant la parole, dit: Donnez \u00e0 la premi\u00e8re l\u2019enfant qui vit, et ne le faites point mourir. C\u2019est elle qui est sa m\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3","name":"1 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.28","name":"1 Rois 3:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.26","name":"1 Rois 3:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.28","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 3:28","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.003.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.004.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.3.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Tout Isra\u00ebl apprit le jugement que le roi avait prononc\u00e9. Et l\u2019on craignit le roi, car on vit que la sagesse de Dieu \u00e9tait en lui pour le diriger dans ses jugements.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3","name":"1 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.4.1","name":"1 Rois 4:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.4.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.27","name":"1 Rois 3:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.3.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fbcbb5706.48214317');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbcbb5706.48214317\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fbcbb5706.48214317","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fbcbb5706.48214317'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbcbb5706.48214317\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}